{"tid":1418732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再吵前線勇武點點點 其實可以達成幾個共識","createTime":"2019-08-05T20:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T20:43:42.000Z","uid":235465,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"986b436788cf1e0c3dc66be30a48f9ec1f313bbd","tid":1418732,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:03:51.000Z","msg":"1:不合作運動或遇見異見者時保持冷靜 隨非人地出手 否則唔好主動攻擊人<br />\n<ins>盡量避免互屌 粗口 <span style=\"color: red;\">PR</span>好重要</ins><br />\n<br />\n2:用唔用火<br />\n火我覺得整火牆之類確保撒退路線 OK無問題 <span style=\"color: red;\">但確保唔會燒親附近店鋪或者人</span><br />\n但燒屋 燒其他地方就不了 重點係<span style=\"color: red;\">無意義</span><br />\n你又燒然後call消防黎熄 然後又點火 有咩意義 只會麻煩到消防員<br />\n<br />\n3:對黑社會<br />\n事實上我覺得用索帶拘捕算最有效 最避免暴力場面<br />\n但如果無索帶 以武制暴 或者如果人多佢地好多就搵人禁住佢 或者打暈佢可能會有效好多<br />\n見得多li D 場面其他人都會反感"},{"pid":"13b2f74df3b27c891c29c074ff95c10249549690","tid":1418732,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:06:41.000Z","msg":"仲有 希望唔好再用鐳射光照正常人 同埋有人影相可以叫手足戴翻口罩<br />\n或者 &quot;唔好意思 可唔可以唔好影&quot;<br />\n當然情緒失控會理解<br />\n但PR好重要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec1d14d82685490cbc7577f9edf9009fdc4545b","tid":1418732,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70761ede80e876892f1c22c7ef5b77716f8a6d14","tid":1418732,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5fb8d078b0d70a7dc8137e5a2a17bf8cde3c62","tid":1418732,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/k